title: Backpack Charger
detail: Imagine never having to worry about finding the nearest outlet!
extended_details: Since students are always carrying their backpacks and always in need of outlets to charge their electronic devices, our plan is to design a backpack charger. This backpack will have built in chargers that use a gyroscope or kinetic energy (of students walking to or from class) in order to supply power.
